    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining Henderson's Relish</strong>, <strong>ketchup </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>mayo </strong>(save the rest for later!) in a bowl – this is your <strong>Marie Rose sauce</strong></p>",
