    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s] and remove the stone[s] using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin[s] using a spoon and mash with a fork</p>",
