    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining mayo</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong> and <strong>chopped chives </strong>to a separate bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>roasted garlic & chive mayo</strong></p>",
