    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill the <strong>toasted ciabatta halves </strong>with the <strong>reserved salad</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>crispy jumbo prawns</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>Marie Rose sauce </strong>and<strong> </strong>a dollop of <strong>mashed avocado</strong> <strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> crispy jumbo prawn cocktail sarnie</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> smoky paprika chips </strong>and the <strong>salad</strong> to the side with the <strong>roasted garlic & chive mayo </strong>spooned over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
